             <example>
             <code>数据源添加方式</code>
             <code>
            1.此处代码示例：获取现有的json文件
            var uri = new System.Uri(Path.Combine(Environment.WebRootPath, "report_modules/Content", "nwind.json"), System.UriKind.Relative);
            var dataConnection = new JsonDataConnection(new UriJsonSource(uri)) { StoreConnectionNameOnly = true, Name = "Default (JSON)" };
            connections.Add(dataConnection.Name, dataConnection.CreateConnectionString());
            2.界面中定义json
            {"Products": [{"ProductID": 1,"ProductName": "sie" }]}
             </code>
             </example>
